      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">3</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 67.1 - 老子 67.3</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 67.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>天下皆謂我道大，似不肖。夫唯大，</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>All the world says that, while my Dao is great, it yet appears to be inferior (to other systems of teaching).</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="laozi-chapter-067__align-002">
      <prop type="x-work-id">laozi</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-id">laozi-chapter-067</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-unit">chapter</prop>
      <prop type="x-segment-type">sentence</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-granularity">grouped</prop>
      <prop type="x-is-coarse-alignment">false</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-type">exact_or_near_exact</prop>
      <prop type="x-confidence">1.00</prop>
      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">2</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 67.4 - 老子 67.5</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 67.2</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>故似不肖。若肖，</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Now it is just its greatness that makes it seem to be inferior.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="laozi-chapter-067__align-003">
      <prop type="x-work-id">laozi</prop>
