      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 67.14 - 老子 67.16</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 67.10 - 老子 67.11</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>不敢為天下先，故能成器長。今舍慈且勇，</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>shrinking from taking precedence of others, I can become a vessel of the highest honour. Now-a-days they give up gentleness and are all for being bold;</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
