      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 67.19 - 老子 67.21</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 67.14 - 老子 67.15</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>死矣！夫慈以戰則勝，以守則固。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>- (of all which the end is) death. Gentleness is sure to be victorious even in battle, and firmly to maintain its ground.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
